CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1953, pg. 12 reads: "Emcee and Mrs. Stevenson...Roland Sawyer and Mrs. James Stevenson took important parts in the Cotillion; he as emcee while she presented the debutantes to the audience. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Roland Sawyer and Mrs. James Stevenson, standing in Syria Mosque for the 1953 Alpha Kappa Alpha cotillion
